This paper is about a framework for hyperparameter optimization (HPO) in machine learning. The most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on improving the performance of machine learning models. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these areas are closely related to machine learning and often involve HPO.
